high_descs: Turn around.  Head towards the sink.  Turn right and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and take the cup that is in the microwave out.
Turn Right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Put the cup to the left of the wine bottle.  Shut the fridge.  Open the fridge and take the cup out.
Turn left and go to the microwave. Put the cup in the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave and shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Take the cup out of the microwave, put it in the fridge, back in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Take the cup from the microwave.
Go to the fridge to your right.
Chill the cup in the fridge.
Go to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Put the cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the sink, turn right towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, take the cup out of it, and close the microwave.
Head towards the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the cup to the left of the bottle, close the fridge, let the cup cool, and then take the cup out of the fridge.
Turn left and head towards the microwave on your right.
Open the microwave, place the cup back inside, and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the cup inside the microwave.
